OL,7,FThe Welsh Ambulance Service said in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "We were called at 3.22pm
OL,9,Fto an incident on Cardiff Road, Barry.
OL,11,F"We sent an emergency ambulance and
OL,12,Fthe Hazardous Area Response Team to
OL,13,Fthe scene, where crews were also
OL,14,Fsupported by an operational commander.
OL,16,F"No patients reported."
