OL,3,C'Chemical incident' in Barry as
OL,4,Cresidents told to shut windows and
OL,5,Cdoors
OL,7,F"In collaboration with the South Wales
OL,8,FFire and Rescue Service Barry
OL,9,Fresidents were advised to close doors
OL,10,Fand windows as a precaution.
OL,12,F"The cause of the release was quickly
OL,13,Fidentified and contained. At 16.50 the
OL,14,Fall clear signal was given, and shared
OL,15,Fwith the community.
OL,17,F"The Dow Emergency Management Team and
OL,18,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,19,Fhave been stood down.
